1
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,999
You've been staring at the screen for ages.

2
00:00:07,233 --> 00:00:08,766
Don't just sit there watching.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:12,099
Go follow, like, and upvote.

4
00:00:12,433 --> 00:00:14,766
I want that one-click triple combo from you.

5
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:19,532
Right now.

6
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:32,803
[Calamity Arc — FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™Episode 37]
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

7
00:00:35,092 --> 00:00:38,480
Holy Sect Master,

8
00:00:39,767 --> 00:00:44,599
You've made me suffer so much.

9
00:00:46,933 --> 00:00:50,299
I will have my revenge.

10
00:00:56,767 --> 00:01:00,466
I'll slaughter every last member of the Heavenly Saint Sect!

11
00:01:03,267 --> 00:01:07,466
I'll kill you all!

12
00:01:15,667 --> 00:01:17,832
Kill you all!

13
00:01:27,433 --> 00:01:29,466
Could the Heavenly Demon Cult Leader have gone to the God-Severing Mountain Range?

14
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,399
Isn't he one of the abandoned people?

15
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,032
Isn't he afraid of being shot down by the Profound Gear Crossbows?

16
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:41,832
Perhaps there's a path to survival hidden there.

17
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:45,332
Send the bugs to scout ahead.

18
00:02:06,167 --> 00:02:07,632
What a shame.

19
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:11,432
This female is actually quite beautiful.

20
00:02:32,533 --> 00:02:33,533
The root demon made too much noise.

21
00:02:33,567 --> 00:02:34,666
It's drawn the pursuers over.

22
00:02:35,833 --> 00:02:40,766
Holy Cult Leader, I will kill you!

23
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:44,866
And wipe out the entire Heavenly Saint Sect!

24
00:02:49,567 --> 00:02:52,566
Demon, what grudge do you hold against the Heavenly Demon Cult?

25
00:02:54,733 --> 00:02:59,099
They sealed this little lady here for six hundred years.

26
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:03,366
My hatred for them runs as deep as the sea.

27
00:03:03,867 --> 00:03:07,066
Master, if you can topple this stone stele and rescue me...

28
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:11,066
I will repay you with my body.

29
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,132
You need not follow me in cultivating Zen.

30
00:03:16,167 --> 00:03:17,766
Just help me kill the Heavenly Demon Cult Leader.

31
00:03:17,867 --> 00:03:18,999
And I shall release you.

32
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:24,632
Such petty fox tricks are enough to bewitch your heart?

33
00:03:25,033 --> 00:03:26,499
The Heavenly Demon Cult follows the demonic path.

34
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:29,399
Any demon they suppress must be a righteous one.

35
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:32,399
We'll need a guide on our journey to the Great Ruins.

36
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:37,399
Everyone, help me push down these demon-suppressing steles.

37
00:03:37,467 --> 00:03:39,066
And free this fellow cultivator.

38
00:04:05,533 --> 00:04:09,432
Thank you, Master.

39
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:13,132
I can finally eat people again.

40
00:04:14,367 --> 00:04:19,232
I can finally eat people again!

41
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:30,832
This is bad.

42
00:04:31,067 --> 00:04:35,499
That demon was deliberately sealed here by the Heavenly Demon Cult Leader to trap us!

43
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:31,099
Little Red, lure it toward the Profound Gear Crossbows.

44
00:05:57,633 --> 00:05:59,299
We've successfully drawn the demon away.

45
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,032
It didn't harm the people of Yan Kang.

46
00:06:01,067 --> 00:06:02,799
That's a blessing in itself.

47
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,999
Even a divine artifact couldn't subdue it.

48
00:06:16,567 --> 00:06:18,232
How is that possible?

49
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,099
Up ahead...

50
00:06:45,467 --> 00:06:47,499
lies the Great Ruins.

51
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,332
This heavenly disaster is a warning from the gods.

52
00:08:16,533 --> 00:08:18,232
It seems to target only Yan Kang.

53
00:08:18,467 --> 00:08:20,999
Come to think of it, ever since I started following Master,

54
00:08:21,233 --> 00:08:23,566
it's been many years since I last returned to the Great Ruins.

55
00:08:27,367 --> 00:08:28,732
Ruins...

56
00:08:28,967 --> 00:08:31,999
Could there still be gods and demons here?

57
00:08:32,233 --> 00:08:33,399
Some died in battle.

58
00:08:33,733 --> 00:08:35,066
Others were sealed away.

59
00:08:35,233 --> 00:08:36,599
But when darkness falls,

60
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,266
they will rise once more.

61
00:08:38,667 --> 00:08:40,866
There's a saying everyone in the Great Ruins knows:

62
00:08:41,167 --> 00:08:43,566
Don't go out after dark.

63
00:08:45,667 --> 00:08:47,399
What does darkness matter?

64
00:08:47,667 --> 00:08:51,699
My Heaven World has already been destroyed and plunged into total darkness.

65
00:08:51,967 --> 00:08:54,966
In the dark, I thrive like a fish in water.

66
00:08:57,233 --> 00:08:58,233
You don't believe me?

67
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:01,332
Come nightfall, I'll take a stroll and show you.

68
00:09:01,356 --> 00:09:21,156
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

69
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,766
The root demon has been released.

70
00:09:23,067 --> 00:09:24,132
Who could be this stupid?

71
00:09:33,467 --> 00:09:36,899
Who did this?

72
00:09:40,533 --> 00:09:42,099
This demon really is courting death,

73
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,732
rampaging wildly through the Great Ruins.

74
00:09:47,167 --> 00:09:49,232
The Great Ruins hold far too many mysterious powers.

75
00:09:49,633 --> 00:09:51,199
Even Grandpa Village Chief

76
00:09:51,767 --> 00:09:53,766
wouldn't act so recklessly.

77
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:07,632
It's fine. The Great Ruins are always like this.

78
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,766
Some ruins hide gods and monsters within.

79
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:12,999
Just remember to burn incense and pray, and you'll be safe.

80
00:10:13,733 --> 00:10:16,666
That root demon probably accidentally disturbed one of the ruins

81
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:18,066
and provoked the deity inside.

82
00:10:18,933 --> 00:10:20,366
The Great Ruins have no king or laws.

83
00:10:20,733 --> 00:10:21,999
So no matter who you meet,

84
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,599
you must always show proper respect.

85
00:10:23,733 --> 00:10:25,132
Otherwise, if you offend the wrong person,

86
00:10:25,267 --> 00:10:26,332
you could easily get killed.

87
00:10:27,133 --> 00:10:30,599
This is too dangerous. I want to go back to Heaven World.

88
00:10:31,167 --> 00:10:34,499
What kind of mortal realm is this broken world of yours?

89
00:10:34,533 --> 00:10:36,232
It's full of demons, monsters, gods, and spirits everywhere!

90
00:10:37,067 --> 00:10:38,366
Fine, I won't invade, okay?

91
00:10:38,433 --> 00:10:39,566
Just let me go.

92
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:42,566
I want to go home.

93
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,366
Once you learn the rules of the Great Ruins,

94
00:10:45,567 --> 00:10:47,999
you'll find it's actually much safer than Yan Kang Kingdom.

95
00:10:48,433 --> 00:10:49,433
If you don't believe me, ask Ling'er.

96
00:10:50,467 --> 00:10:51,566
Young Master came out this time

97
00:10:51,633 --> 00:10:53,299
precisely to gain experience in Yan Kang Kingdom.

98
00:10:53,433 --> 00:10:55,799
Training in the Great Ruins doesn't even count.

99
00:10:55,833 --> 00:10:57,999
That just shows how dangerous Yan Kang truly is.

100
00:10:58,367 --> 00:10:59,266
Don't worry.

101
00:10:59,367 --> 00:11:01,132
The Great Ruins are very safe.

102
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:03,266
You'll be fine as long as you stay with Young Master.

103
00:11:04,867 --> 00:11:07,666
I was only looking for a low-level world

104
00:11:07,733 --> 00:11:09,666
where my people could settle down.

105
00:11:10,167 --> 00:11:13,099
The Heaven World is already finished.

106
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:15,032
If I keep fighting you with blood and lives,

107
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:17,666
we'll truly go extinct.

108
00:11:17,667 --> 00:11:18,032
We'll truly go extinct.

109
00:11:30,367 --> 00:11:33,099
Young Master seems quite pitiful, actually.

110
00:11:33,633 --> 00:11:34,932
He's only a strand of consciousness.

111
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:37,232
His true body is still in the Heaven World.

112
00:11:37,367 --> 00:11:39,566
If he really wanted to keep searching for other worlds,

113
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,999
why would he insist on sending this consciousness back?

114
00:11:42,233 --> 00:11:43,999
Not a single word from that guy can be trusted.

115
00:11:51,867 --> 00:11:53,299
I can't fly anymore...

116
00:11:58,167 --> 00:12:01,366
Dragon Fatty told you ages ago to lose some weight.

117
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:03,832
Young Master!

118
00:12:04,167 --> 00:12:04,832
Young Master is back!

119
00:12:04,867 --> 00:12:05,867
Young Master!

120
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:07,032
Young Master is back!

121
00:12:09,333 --> 00:12:10,099
Young Master!

122
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:13,166
How does Yan Kang Kingdom compare to our Great Ruins?

123
00:12:14,233 --> 00:12:16,266
Yan Kang is far more chaotic than the Great Ruins.

124
00:12:16,567 --> 00:12:19,199
Rebellions and wars every day—it's total chaos.

125
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,832
Definitely not a good place.

126
00:12:21,433 --> 00:12:22,433
Indeed.

127
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:25,499
Not long ago, many refugees fled into the Great Ruins.

128
00:12:25,867 --> 00:12:28,266
They said they escaped because of the snow disaster.

129
00:12:28,667 --> 00:12:29,866
It's good that Young Master is back.

130
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:32,466
After all, home is still the safest.

131
00:12:41,167 --> 00:12:43,166
Young Master! Young Master is back!

132
00:12:43,733 --> 00:12:44,399
Granny.

133
00:12:45,767 --> 00:12:47,232
Has the City Lord returned?

134
00:12:47,467 --> 00:12:50,299
The City Lord came by a while ago and then left.

135
00:12:51,433 --> 00:12:52,433
Will Young Master be staying?

136
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:53,932
I'll prepare the rooms right away.

137
00:12:54,367 --> 00:12:54,966
No need.

138
00:12:55,533 --> 00:12:56,533
The New Year is approaching.

139
00:12:56,767 --> 00:12:58,266
I'll head back to the village first.

140
00:12:58,533 --> 00:13:00,866
You've eaten and lazed around enough. Ready to move?

141
00:13:00,933 --> 00:13:02,099
Let's get going.

142
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,400
Xian Qing'er.

143
00:13:14,267 --> 00:13:16,066
The cowherd boy has returned in glory!

144
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,500
Was it fun outside?

145
00:13:18,167 --> 00:13:20,732
It was okay... except everyone kept trying to kill me wherever I went.

146
00:13:21,567 --> 00:13:24,399
By the way, has Little Lai come looking for you?

147
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,399
Good fortune and great profit!

148
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,366
He never made it here.

149
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:31,799
What bad thing did you do to get chased like that?

150
00:13:32,933 --> 00:13:35,699
Probably because I'm just too outstanding and people are jealous.

151
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:41,266
I'll come visit your village for New Year's when I have time.

152
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:44,532
Just don't let your folks kill me.

153
00:13:44,867 --> 00:13:45,867
Okay.

154
00:14:03,767 --> 00:14:07,232
Granny, Grandpa, I'm back!

155
00:14:16,733 --> 00:14:18,799
I went through so much hardship to rush back.

156
00:14:19,233 --> 00:14:20,999
Why is no one paying attention to me?

157
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:22,799
Trying to prank me again?

158
00:14:24,167 --> 00:14:24,866
Mute Grandpa.

159
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:28,232
Medicine Grandpa, I see you!

160
00:14:28,233 --> 00:14:29,599
Horse Grandpa.

161
00:14:29,833 --> 00:14:30,899
Village Chief Grandpa.

162
00:14:30,933 --> 00:14:32,332
Deaf Grandpa.

163
00:14:32,333 --> 00:14:33,099
Butcher Grandpa.

164
00:14:33,267 --> 00:14:34,332
Tumor Grandpa.

165
00:14:34,333 --> 00:14:35,566
Blind Grandpa.

166
00:14:35,633 --> 00:14:38,966
Granny...

167
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:44,366
Strange... where did everyone go?

168
00:14:56,067 --> 00:14:59,566
The Medicine Master and I will take the Heavenly Demon Cult's Patriarch and Law Enforcement Elder

169
00:14:59,567 --> 00:15:01,166
into the darkness for a trip.

170
00:15:01,267 --> 00:15:02,632
We'll scout out Carefree Village.

171
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:05,899
If anyone returns, help the Medicine Master feed the bugs.

172
00:15:06,067 --> 00:15:07,966
The Village Chief and the others still haven't come back.

173
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:09,732
The Blind One and I will go look for them.

174
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:18,599
Those old fellows might have run into danger.

175
00:15:18,733 --> 00:15:21,099
The Horse Master and I will also head to Carefree Village.

176
00:15:22,900 --> 00:15:23,732
Mu'er.

177
00:15:24,067 --> 00:15:26,599
I'll go bring those old things back for the New Year.

178
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,666
Don't wander around.

179
00:15:29,233 --> 00:15:32,232
If you see the Deaf One, make him something to eat.

180
00:15:32,533 --> 00:15:34,099
He's about to starve to death.

181
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,699
Granny, the grandpas, and the Patriarch

182
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,999
have all gone to search for Carefree Village.

183
00:15:44,986 --> 00:15:52,793
[Root Demon: Its true form is a mass of roots. By absorbing divine blood and demonic blood, it evolves into a great demon, gaining immense power. Extremely dangerous, it disguises itself as a woman during hunts, using this form to lure prey into its trap.]

184
00:15:52,817 --> 00:15:59,856
[Great Ruins Rules: The Great Ruins are desolate and strange, filled with sinister anomalies; there are no nations or laws, and to survive one must follow its unique rules. Here, strength is everything—the strong prey on the weak, and only the fittest survive, with all one seizes becoming their own. At the same time, in this land overrun with gods and monsters, one must observe proper rites: by day, offer incense and pray when encountering temples to remain safe; by night, never go out, and never act recklessly within the dark ruins. These rules are not written laws, but the boundaries of survival discovered through the lives of those who came before.]

185
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:30,180
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

